OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Evil' child abuser guilty 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fof girl's 1992 murder      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A convicted child abuser has been found
OL,6, guilty of brutally murdering a         
OL,7, seven-year-old girl more than 30 years 
OL,8, ago.                                   
OL,10,FNikki Allan was repeatedly hit with a  
OL,11,Fbrick and stabbed dozens of times      
OL,12,Fbefore her body was abandoned in a     
OL,13,Fderelict building near her home in     
OL,14,FSunderland in October 1992.            
OL,16,FDavid Boyd, 55, from Stockton-on-Tees, 
OL,17,Fwas convicted at Newcastle Crown Court 
OL,18,Fafter a three-week trial.              
OL,20,FNikki's mother said the "evil man" had 
OL,21,F"slipped through the net" for decades. 
